description: In the realm of Arklain the war between the gods and demons has finally ended. The clan of the Immortals now rule. They've demanded that each clan give up their most powerful member, called a 'Kether' or chosen one. The Immortals will control the Kethers, and make certain they are never used to wage war again. The Kether Taris is controlled by a brutal and insane Immortal named Aralan. Aralan quickly becomes obsessed with the angelic creature. He tries to pull Taris into his mad fantasies. Also in this book, Summoned by a Demon by Yamila Abraham and Studio Kosaru. A young holyman is summoned to a mining planet to help the inhabitants deal with a demonic presence. He finds out quickly he's actually been lured to the planet to be an offering for the Demon General terrorizing the people.
name: Vol. 1

description: The spoiled Prince Anel must travel without military escort to a neighboring kingdom where tensions run high. Sastre, an honorable Guardian, is brought in to be Anel's only protection for the journey. Anel is enchanted by his noble bodyguard, but Sastre becomes more interested in Kaleth, the spirited servant and lover of Prince Anel. Kaleth is forced to disguise himself as the prince to be a decoy for his enemies. Sastre duty is to protect Prince Anel, but in his heart he'd rather keep the decoy safe from harm.
name: Vol. 1

description: The gorgeous surfer Shawn needs to pass Marine Biology or else he'll flunk out of college. Luckily for him, the cute nerd Alan is dying to learn how to surf. The two are brought into each others' worlds and romantic sparks fly. It seems like a dream for Alan until Shawn's former boyfriend Clay gives him a harsh reality check. Clay warns that Shawn is just using Alan. He'll drop him the second he passes his test. He also hints about Shawn's dark side, which may have something to do with the injury that made Clay have to stop surfing. Can such a mismatched couple really be happy? Or is Alan just diving into trouble? By the same artist as the popular Zesty web comic!
name: Vol. 1

description: Patrick and Alan are two navy sailors deeply in love. Their romance is shattered by the conniving sailor Ian, who also loves Patrick. Ian uses the cover of a battle to shoot Alan when his back is turned. The captain of the pirates they're battling orders for the wounded Alan to be captured as they withdraw. Alan is forced to join the crew of the Adventurer under the pirate captain Bergardoux, who was impressed with the military prowess he saw Alan display on the navy vessel. Though Alan resists at first, the Captain's overwhelming charm and Alan's own thirst for adventure eventually causes him to relish the pirate life. Fate brings Patrick and Alan face to face again, but this time as enemies. Patrick is thrilled the love of his life is still alive, but horrified to see he's become a pirate.
name: Vol. 1

description: The saga of a British Naval officer turned Pirate continues. Alan Falconer is now Captain of the pirate ship Adventurer, and he's convinced his lover Patrick to join them. Alan longs for things to go back to the way they were between him and Patrick, but Patrick can't forget that Alan had an affair with the former pirate captain. It doesn't help that Alan has them on a mission to avenge Captain Begardoux's death. The love that Alan still has for his lost captain is more than Patrick can bear. Especially when he gave up such a stellar naval career just to be with him. How can they face the murderous pirate Van Holstein when they stand divided?
name: Vol. 2

description: When three ruthless fire demons come to terrorize the monk Hakuin's village he's forced to seek help from Fuyu, the snow demon who tormented him a year ago. Fuyu is thrilled to see his beautiful monk again. He'll defeat the demons only if Hakuin becomes his willing slave. Fuyu realizes too late that the fire demons are out of his league. Even worse, the lead demon thinks the fey Fuyu would make a nice slave in his own right. When Fuyu is put in the same position he put Hakuin a year ago he starts to realize the error of his ways. Maybe, in time, he can even be redeemed to his beloved monk. Also in this book, a pacifist is forced to bring an assassin to a rival lord. It doesn't help that the assassin is part of the group who wiped out the pacifist's race. (So why are they sleeping together?)
name: Vol. 1

description: The Winter Demon, Fuyu, and the Monk, Hakuin, seek the healer for Kyoko, only to learn he works exclusively for the royalty of his village. He'll only heal Kyoko if Fuyu puts on a magic show for the prince, and Fuyu will only put on a magic show if his Hakuin accepts him in his bed.
name: Vol. 2

description:
The winter demon Fuyu meets the incubus Figaru at long last! Fuyu and the monk Hakuin must see the holyman Shidan to fix Fuyu's weapon. Fuyu is terrified of Shidan's demon apprentice Figaru. The incubus needs a mate to renew his powers, and he thinks Fuyu is gorgeous.

Hakuin and Shidan have to see a priestess to get the weapon fixed. She doesn't like demons, so Fuyu and Figaru have to stay behind. After one 'incident' already Shidan locks Figaru in a sacred ring to keep him away from Fuyu. But days pass, and Hakuin and Shidan not returned.

Fuyu is powerless without his weapon. He needs Figaru's mighty powers to rescue Hakuin. Figaru isn't so mighty lately. He needs a mate badly. The most anticipated volume of the series!
name: Vol. 3

description: The final volume of the hit series! Fuyu seeks Dr. Takuma to treat Hakuin's badly infected wounds. The Spring Demon Ryuuto is still wooing Takuma when Fuyu arrives. Fuyu and Hakuin find themselves in the position of matchmakers as Hakuin's injuries heal. Just when things seem to be going well, there's a misunderstanding. Now Ryuuto has angered them all. Hakuin decides their old friend Figaru is just the one to teach this evil demon a lesson. Meanwhile, Hakuin's injuries heal, and it's time for him to keep his promise to Fuyu.
name: Vol. 4

description:
In this issue:
  1. L'uomo dei ghiacci, by Stefano Piani &Francesco Bastianoni
  2. Il ritorno di Janus, by Antonio Serra & Elena Pianta
  3. La donna tigre, by Riccardo Secchi & Andrea Bormida
name: L'uomo dei ghiacci

description: The final A3 tabloid sized issue of Topper.

Hughie returns to The Boys after his hiatus in Scotland and is immediately dragged out on a call with Butcher. A transvestite hooker has been beaten to death and Butcher suspects The Seven's Jack from Jupiter. The only way to be sure though is to go see Doctor Peculiar, a shady figure who caters to the Supes' kinky desires.

Determined that things are going to change, Hughie demands that Butcher not keep him in the dark if he wants Hughie to remain on the team. Butcher tentatively agrees based on how Hugie handles himself on this case.

Back at The Seven's HQ, Jack is quizzed about their suspicions over his role in the death. They're concerned that he may be jeopardizing the Homelander's coming plan.
name: The Big Ride, Part 1

description: Four lives are fatally intertwined behind the scenes of a small Venice theater. An actor, a writer, a theater director and a teenage boy are drawn into a dangerous game of Chinese boxes played partway between dream and reality. Alessandro Leone is a young and brilliant actor. Luca Arcadi turned his back on his wealthy family to become a writer. Adrian Hoeg is a famous Danish theater director. Marco Amedei is nineteen year old lead actor. The lives of these four men intertwine amid the setting of a Venice theater. They find themselves drawn into in their own drama, filled with romance, deception, and anguish. It's said the only difference between a comedy and tragedy is the ending. Will this simply be a comedy of errors? Or will the ending be filled with futile deaths?
name: Vol. 1

description: A brand new anthology series of guys in love with guys. First, prisoners of a medieval circus unite against their wicked ringmaster. Then a tale of forbidden love between members of two rival gangs in modern Tokyo. The final tale is of a boy who escapes two sadistic hillbilly captors and recovers from their torture with the help of a romantically vulnerable cop.
name: Vol. 1

description: Tim is a young victim of a genetic experiment. Now the troubled child is able to escape his persecutors, but not yet out of danger. His dramatic case, in the past, was of interest for Nathan Never, and will still be the melancholic Alfa agent to follow the adventures of the unfortunate human guinea pig in his difficult present. He will try to have justice, in a lethal battle with the cruel Savage, a member of the secret services and ruthless murderer.
name: Uccidete Nathan never

description: Sunn idolizes his chieftain brother Raff, even if Raff treats him more like a concubine than brother. Sunn thinks the war Raff wages on the "barbarian" tribe is righteous. That is until he meets a beautiful captive of theirs named Ciclo.
name: Vol. 2

description: This is yaoi at its most extreme: graphic scenes of loving between a college professor and his student, a bar-hopper & some thugs who kidnap him, members of a corrupt soccer team and a tentacle monster who's hot for a pair of twin bishounen. Nothing is left to the imagination!
name: Vol. 1

description: Yaoi Hentai is back with a whole new volume of romantic yaoi smut. All new artists bring you four hot stories of hardcore guy on guy loving. First, an Elizabethan dandy is cursed to be the love slave of anyone who plays his violin. Next enjoy a science fiction story of a prince who endures trials of sexual pain and pleasure at the hands of his idol, the emperor of a sexually depraved planet. Fans of Yaoi Press' PINNED! graphic novel get to see a hardcore love scene between Renegade and Synn. This short vignette takes place immediately after the last page of PINNED! volume 1. And of course, Trach the tentacle monster rounds out the book in his second sex-filled adventure.
name: Vol. 2

description: In Vol. 3 of the ultra popular, kinky, sex-full Yaoi Hentai you'll see tentacle monster Trach nailing an unsuspecting bus rider, a poor bishonen with his wiener caught in a fence hole and the perv friend who helps, a yaoi take on the 'Aristocrats' joke, and more!
name: Vol. 3

description: The hit series continues! Volume 4 of the sexiest yaoi anthology going brings in all new talent, including famous comic creator Donna Barr! Stories include a nobleman succumbing to pleasure in the desert, and a space general losing control of a prisoner for even more pleasure. A young sorcerer in training wants to be initiated by the darkest sorcerer in the world. And finally-Trach the tentacle monster is ticked off! His fellow sex monsters are being rounded up to be used in vile sexual acts--er wait a minute--where does he sign up!
name: Vol. 4

description: Meet Zesty Tastee, flamboyant gay playboy and heir to the Tastee Corporation fortune. That's what the world knows of him, but Zesty is also Magpie, the corporate saboteur who fights against his father's corrupt business schemes. Zesty's evil tycoon dad is out to destroy an entire rainforest, and he's joined up with a mysterious sect of ninjas to help keep 'Magpie' from interfering. Prince Ander is the sect agent on the case, and Zesty has love at first sight for this dreamy ninja master. Zesty can't understand why anyone as noble as Prince would ever work with his father. His mission is to find out the secret of the rain forest, and win Prince's heart in the process!
name: Vol. 1

description: It's chaos in Zestyland! Zesty flees to the country his dad bought him to escape his beloved ninja agent Prince. Prince wants to let him go, but the sect is threatening to send the nastiest agent they've got after Zesty in Prince's place. So Prince is off to Zestyland, broken leg and all. If he thought Zesty was wacky, wait until he meets Zesty's maniacal mother! Meanwhile, Zesty's cousin Sterling is posing as the daughter of the Sect's mountain guide to find out why Prince's dad is leading the sect on an elaborate mountain expedition. Just his luck--the big, gruff sect agent Whiskey has a crush on him. How can he escape this guy when the mountain guide he's working with thinks it's a good joke to promise Whiskey his hand in marriage?
name: Vol. 2

description:
Abandoned as a baby and raised in an orphanage, the kind-hearted high-schooler Yuki Sakuragi is driven by a need to find the reason for his existence. Plagued by mysterious dreams, Yuki also possesses the strange ability to read the deepest, darkest thoughts of anyone he touches. As both the dreams and his powers intensify, there appears before him a beautiful young man named "Zess," whose face tugs on Yuki's memory. He warns Yuki not to venture outside on Walpurgis Night, the eve of the blood-red moon, which invites death. But when Yuki's compassion leads him to disobey Zess's order, has Yuki carelessly thrown his life away before he's even given himself the chance to find out the very reason for it?

Chapter Titles

  • Story 1: Time, Set in Motion
  • Story 2: Eternl Investigation
  • Story 3: Walpurgis Night
  • Story 4: Irretrievable Days, White Tomorrows
  • Story 5: New Encounters
  • Story 6: Suspicion
  • Story 7: The Line Between Light and Despair
  • Story 8: Twilight Hall
  • Story 8.5: Elegant Mornings at Twilight Hall
  • Story 9: Rising Curtain, Cresting Wave
  • Story 10: Brand Zess
  • Story 11: Scars
  • Extra: Fun for Takashiro-sama
  • Extra: I Have an Objection to the Script
name: Vol. 1

description: The Empress Ann survived the battle with Artisia and still threatens all the infinite universes. To stop her, Nemo ( in a new version, "in the flesh" ) and Artisia leave with the Nautilus to get to Arret , the planet at the center of the multiverse , the place where Ann Never and Gabriel came after leaving Earth.
name: L'ultimo viaggio del Nautilus
